From: Miklos Szeredi <miklos@szeredi.hu>
Subject: [FUSE] Add basic file operations
Patch-mainline: 2.6.12-rc-mm

This patch adds the file operations of FUSE.

The following operations are added:

 o open
 o flush
 o release
 o fsync
 o readpage
 o commit_write

